\[h(\theta) = \frac{v^2 \sin^2 \theta}{2g}.\]We want to find the area of the region enclosed by the graph of $h(\theta)$ as $\theta$ ranges from $0^\circ$ to $180^\circ.$

[asy]
unitsize (3 cm);

real g, v;

g = 1;
v = 1;

draw((0,0)--(pi/2,1)--(pi,0));
draw((pi/2,1)--(pi/2,0));

